  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/5f66cd277f0273e03015da89993991dc.poster.avif?t=1764123975\" width=609 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/5f66cd277f0273e03015da89993991dc.webm?t=1764123975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>- The whole point of the game is to collect the entire collection of tapes hidden throughout the map and complete them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/41c0fe55143ef451270543ea1352000b.poster.avif?t=1764123975\" width=358 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/41c0fe55143ef451270543ea1352000b.webm?t=1764123975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>- Look for hidden tapes and play them on your TV with a set-top box. When you start the mini-game on the TV, you can split into teams and even play alone against everyone to show your superiority. Each cassette contains a unique mini-game that can be played with or without friends. Each mini-game may change the mechanics of the game, so there is no core mechanic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/3995051f64bfc7d19d63464a8f51e1c3.poster.avif?t=1764123975\" width=493 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/3995051f64bfc7d19d63464a8f51e1c3.webm?t=1764123975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>- You appear in an open world, where we recommend inviting your friends. Explore locations in search of tapes that can be hidden anywhere. Each cassette contains a unique mini-game, which depends on its location.<br><i><u>\"There are unique tapes that only a select few will find.\"</u></i><br>- The tapes you find can be played on the TV set-top box to start a mini-game. All mini-games can be completed with your friends.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/5f66cd277f0273e03015da89993991dc.poster.avif?t=1764123975\" width=609 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/5f66cd277f0273e03015da89993991dc.webm?t=1764123975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>- The whole point of the game is to collect the entire collection of tapes hidden throughout the map and complete them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/41c0fe55143ef451270543ea1352000b.poster.avif?t=1764123975\" width=358 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/41c0fe55143ef451270543ea1352000b.webm?t=1764123975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>- Look for hidden tapes and play them on your TV with a set-top box. When you start the mini-game on the TV, you can split into teams and even play alone against everyone to show your superiority. Each cassette contains a unique mini-game that can be played with or without friends. Each mini-game may change the mechanics of the game, so there is no core mechanic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/3995051f64bfc7d19d63464a8f51e1c3.poster.avif?t=1764123975\" width=493 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710420/extras/3995051f64bfc7d19d63464a8f51e1c3.webm?t=1764123975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>- You appear in an open world, where we recommend inviting your friends. Explore locations in search of tapes that can be hidden anywhere. Each cassette contains a unique mini-game, which depends on its location.<br><i><u>\"There are unique tapes that only a select few will find.\"</u></i><br>- The tapes you find can be played on the TV set-top box to start a mini-game. All mini-games can be completed with your friends.",
